"1454","(+/-)  As long as the Fund invests all (or substantially all) of its assets in"
"1455","       a single, registered, open-end management investment company in"
"1456","       accordance with Section 12(d)(1)(E) under the 1940 Act, the Fund does not"
"1457","       pay Funds Management an investment advisory fee. At the time the Fund"
"1458","       invests some of its assets in two or more registered, open-end management"
"1459","       investment companies in accordance with Section 12(d)(1)(G) under the"
"1460","       1940 Act, the Fund shall pay Funds Management an investment advisory fee"
"1461","       of 0.25% for asset allocation services."
"1462","The foregoing fee schedule is agreed to as of March 29, 2013 and shall"
"1463","remain in effect until changed in writing by the parties."
